tly one kind of archived object, the database name stating what it archives, paired with a small archive-retrieving tool. When composite intent retires its source records, the sources are archived and referenced by hash identity from the composite so provenance survives cleanly. CollectRemovalCandidates archives collected records automatically to a default archive surface before hot-store removal, with typed retrieval rather than ad-hoc caller files.] Medium High Zero [archive sema spirit collect-removal-candidates]))])